{% liquid
  assign product = closest.product
  # MOXIE: flags de campaña, 2 fuentes que coexisten (metaobject product_flag, mismo que antes):
  # - product.metafields.custom.flag: asignación directa a un producto puntual (legacy, un producto suelto).
  # - collection.metafields.custom.flag: asignación por colección completa (requiere la MISMA definición
  #   de metafield custom.flag creada también a nivel Collection en el Admin, apuntando al mismo
  #   metaobject product_flag) — un producto puede pertenecer a 2+ colecciones flageadas a la vez, en
  #   ese caso se muestran TODAS, apiladas (ver --stylesheet), sin duplicar si comparten la misma entrada.
  # Prioridad fija acordada con el cliente: Sold out siempre gana > flags (producto + colecciones) > Sale automático.
  assign product_flag = product.metafields.custom.flag.value
%}

{% capture children %}
  {% unless product == blank %}
    {%- if product.available == false -%}
      <div
        class="product-badges product-badges--{{ settings.badge_position }}"
        style="
            --badge-border-radius: {{ settings.badge_corner_radius }}px;
            --badge-font-family: var(--font-{{ settings.badge_font_family }}--family); --badge-font-weight: var(--font-{{ settings.badge_font_family }}--weight); --badge-text-transform: {{ settings.badge_text_transform }};
        "
      >
        <div class="product-badges__badge product-badges__badge--rectangle color-custom-badge-sold-out">
          {{ 'content.product_badge_sold_out' | t }}
        </div>
      </div>
    {%- else -%}
      {% liquid
        assign has_flag = false
        if product_flag != blank
          assign has_flag = true
        endif
        for collection in product.collections
          if collection.metafields.custom.flag.value != blank
            assign has_flag = true
          endif
        endfor
      %}
      {%- if has_flag or product.compare_at_price > product.price -%}
        <div
          class="product-badges product-badges--{{ settings.badge_position }}"
          style="
              --badge-border-radius: {{ settings.badge_corner_radius }}px;
              --badge-font-family: var(--font-{{ settings.badge_font_family }}--family); --badge-font-weight: var(--font-{{ settings.badge_font_family }}--weight); --badge-text-transform: {{ settings.badge_text_transform }};
          "
        >
          {%- liquid
            assign flag_ids_shown = ''
          -%}
          {%- if product_flag != blank -%}
            {%- render 'custom_product-flag-badge', flag: product_flag -%}
            {%- assign flag_ids_shown = flag_ids_shown | append: product_flag.system.id | append: '|' -%}
          {%- endif -%}
          {%- for collection in product.collections -%}
            {%- assign collection_flag = collection.metafields.custom.flag.value -%}
            {%- if collection_flag != blank -%}
              {%- assign flag_marker = collection_flag.system.id | append: '|' -%}
              {%- unless flag_ids_shown contains flag_marker -%}
                {%- render 'custom_product-flag-badge', flag: collection_flag -%}
                {%- assign flag_ids_shown = flag_ids_shown | append: flag_marker -%}
              {%- endunless -%}
            {%- endif -%}
          {%- endfor -%}
          {%- if has_flag == false and product.compare_at_price > product.price -%}
            <div class="product-badges__badge product-badges__badge--rectangle color-custom-badge-sale">
              {{ 'content.product_badge_sale' | t }}
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}
    {%- endif -%}
    {%- comment -%} MOXIE: wishlist mobile, absoluta sobre la imagen (oculta en desktop vía CSS, ver blocks/custom_wishlist.liquid para la versión desktop) {%- endcomment -%}
    {% render 'custom_wishlist-button', product: product, variant: 'mobile' %}
    {%- comment -%}
      MOXIE: el catálogo NafNaf solo maneja la opción Talla, así que se reemplaza el quick-add nativo
      (snippets/quick-add.liquid, que abriría el modal "Choose" para 2+ opciones) por un selector de
      talla propio: overlay inline en hover para desktop, y trigger del modal "Compra rápida" en mobile.
    {%- endcomment -%}
    {% if product.available %}
      {% if settings.quick_add or settings.mobile_quick_add %}
        {% render 'custom_product-card-size-select', product: product, section_id: section.id %}
        {% render 'custom_quick-view-modal', product: product, section_id: section.id, block: block %}
      {% endif %}
    {% endif %}
  {% endunless %}
{% endcapture %}

{% render 'card-gallery', children: children %}

{% # Title and price for the zoomed out grid view %}
<div class="product-grid-view-zoom-out--details">
  {% if product == blank %}
    <h3 class="h4">{{ 'content.product_card_placeholder' | t }}</h3>
  {% else %}
    <h3 class="h4">{{ product.title }}</h3>
  {% endif %}
</div>

{% render 'product-card-gallery-zoom-details-styles' %}
{% render 'product-badges-styles' %}

{% stylesheet %}
  /* MOXIE: el <a ref="cardGalleryLink"> nativo (snippets/card-gallery.liquid) que envuelve
     toda la card no resetea el tap-highlight de WebKit/Chrome mobile — al tocar la card (o
     los overlays absolutos encima: flags, wishlist, "+") el navegador pinta un rectángulo
     azul translúcido sobre toda la card. No se toca el snippet nativo, se resetea acá. */
  .card-gallery a.contents {
    -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
  }

  /* MOXIE: separación e tamaño exactos del Figma para las flags (NEW IN/SALE/SOLD OUT) —
     --badge-inset reemplaza la fórmula nativa basada en --border-radius, min-height/radius
     ajustan el tamaño mínimo del chip. Selector con doble clase para ganarle en
     especificidad a snippets/product-badges-styles.liquid (nativo, no se toca) sin
     depender del orden de bundling de los stylesheets. */
  /* MOXIE: un producto puede traer 2+ flags simultáneas si pertenece a varias colecciones
     flageadas — no hay spec de Figma para este caso (el diseño solo contempla una flag a la
     vez), se apilan verticalmente con un gap chico entre chips. */
  .card-gallery .product-badges {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .card-gallery .product-badges {
      --badge-inset: 18px;
    }

    .card-gallery .product-badges__badge {
      min-height: 21.43px;
    }

    .card-gallery .product-badges__badge--image img {
      height: 21.43px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .card-gallery .product-badges {
      --badge-inset: 24px;
    }

    .card-gallery .product-badges__badge {
      min-height: 22px;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .card-gallery .product-badges__badge--image img {
      height: 22px;
    }
  }

  /* MOXIE: flag con imagen/gif (metaobject product_flag, campo `image`) — alternativa al chip de
     texto, pedido por el cliente ad-hoc (no hay spec de Figma). Alto igual al chip de texto por
     breakpoint (ver arriba), ancho libre según aspect ratio del archivo. */
  .card-gallery .product-badges__badge--image {
    padding: 0;
    background: none;
  }

  .card-gallery .product-badges__badge--image img {
    display: block;
    width: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
  }
{% endstylesheet %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "t:names.product_image",
  "tag": null,
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "t:content.resource_reference_product_media"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "t:content.moxie_quick_add_header"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "low_stock_threshold",
      "label": "t:settings.low_stock_threshold",
      "min": 1,
      "max": 10,
      "step": 1,
      "default": 3,
      "info": "t:info.low_stock_threshold"
    },
    {
      "type": "select",
      "id": "image_ratio",
      "options": [
        {
          "value": "adapt",
          "label": "t:options.auto"
        },
        {
          "value": "portrait",
          "label": "t:options.portrait"
        },
        {
          "value": "square",
          "label": "t:options.square"
        },
        {
          "value": "landscape",
          "label": "t:options.landscape"
        }
      ],
      "default": "portrait",
      "label": "t:settings.aspect_ratio",
      "info": "t:info.aspect_ratio_adjusted"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "t:content.borders"
    },
    {
      "type": "select",
      "id": "border",
      "label": "t:settings.style",
      "options": [
        {
          "value": "none",
          "label": "t:options.none"
        },
        {
          "value": "solid",
          "label": "t:options.solid"
        }
      ],
      "default": "none"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "border_width",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 4,
      "step": 1,
      "unit": "px",
      "label": "t:settings.thickness",
      "default": 1,
      "visible_if": "{{ block.settings.border != 'none' }}"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "border_opacity",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 100,
      "step": 1,
      "unit": "%",
      "label": "t:settings.opacity",
      "default": 100,
      "visible_if": "{{ block.settings.border != 'none' }}"
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "border_color",
      "label": "t:settings.color",
      "placeholder": "t:settings.default",
      "visible_if": "{{ block.settings.border != 'none' }}"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "border_radius",
      "label": "t:settings.border_radius",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 100,
      "step": 1,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "t:content.padding"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "padding-block-start",
      "label": "t:settings.top",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 50,
      "step": 1,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "padding-block-end",
      "label": "t:settings.bottom",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 50,
      "step": 1,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "padding-inline-start",
      "label": "t:settings.left",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 50,
      "step": 1,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "padding-inline-end",
      "label": "t:settings.right",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 50,
      "step": 1,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 0
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "t:names.product_card_media",
      "category": "t:categories.product"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
